			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Lithium Nickel Cobalt Aluminum Oxide, often referred to as NCA, is a type of lithium-ion battery cathode material. It encompasses high energy density processing and is tailored for use in battery applications. NCA is known for its high performance and is compliant with industry standards for use in consumer electronics and electric vehicles. It is produced through a specific synthesis route and originates from the base materials of nickel, cobalt, and aluminum in a lithium matrix. It is commonly available to consumers and industrial entities.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">锂镍钴铝氧化物（通常称为NCA）是一种锂离子电池正极材料。它包含了高能量密度的处理，并专门用于电池应用。NCA以其高性能而著称，并符合消费电子和电动汽车使用的行业标准。该产品通过特定的合成路径制成，源自镍、钴、铝在锂基质中的基本材料。它通常向消费者和工业实体提供。</common:generalComment>
